  "detailed_description": "This game is a Japanese visual novel.<br />\r\nsorry. This game is for Japanese only<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis is a story of anguish and conflict.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAt the age of 30, the unsold actor Ryo Matsumoto is suffering from the idea that the main character does not want to give up his dream and that he should give up his dream.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI don't audition.<br />\r\nThe part-time job doesn't last either.<br />\r\nI don't even have a girlfriend.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEven if he loses his dream and realizes that he is not talented<br />\r\nCan you still dream ...?",
